sub_title: Data Engineer at ASML, Ph.D. Student at the Computer Systems Section, Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam
summary:
Currently a Data Engineer at ASML that is wrapping up his Ph.D. Student at the Computer Systems Section, Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam, with as topic primarily working on scheduling workflows in datacenters.
My publication list can be seen at http://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/v/Versluis:Laurens

projects: [{'title': 'TrapEm', 'date': {'start': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}, 'end': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}}, 'description': "TrapEm is a game created during the Contextproject at my study at the TU Delft. The game keeps track of people walking trough a field via a camera above it. By walking trough the field people create lines and thus forming polygons. While drawing these lines they should avoid the bad guy who is running around. If one creates a line successfully from one side to another, the area is closed and the bad guy can no longer enter it. Once 80% of the field is closed, you win! If the bad guy manages to hit people busy drawing a line 5 times it's game over.\n\nOnce the project was finished, the Science Center of the TU Delft approached us if we could place our game there for the public. Thus now TrapEm will entertain hundreds if not thousands of kids at the Science Center with a permanent place!", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Laurens', 'last_name': 'Versluis', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Data Engineer at ASML, Ph.D. Student at the Computer Systems Section, Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam'}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Pouja Nikray', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Pedram Ardeshirzade', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Ruben Vroegindeweij', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Jesse', 'headline': None}]}, {'title': 'Klockon', 'date': {'start': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}}, 'description': 'Klockon is an event platform that serves students in and around Delft an overview of all events.
